msgid "Psst! Don't tell anyone."
msgstr "Psst! Fortæl det ikke til nogen."

msgid "About psst-secret"
msgstr "Om psst-secret"

msgid ""
"A privacy focused app for sharing secrets securely. We call them whispers."
msgstr ""
"En privatlivsfokuseret app til at dele hemmeligheder sikkert. Vi kalder dem "
"whispers."

msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "Sådan virker det"

msgid ""
"psst-secret ensures that <strong class=\"text-white\">your whispers never "
"exist in plaintext on our server</strong>. All encryption and decryption "
"happens entirely in your browser using the <a href=\"https://"
"developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\" class=\"text-"
"brand-400 underline hover:text-brand-300\" target=\"_blank\">Web Crypto API</"
"a>."
msgstr ""
"psst-secret sikrer, at <strong class=\"text-white\">dine whispers aldrig "
"findes i klartekst på vores server</strong>. Al kryptering og dekryptering "
"foregår udelukkende i din browser ved hjælp af <a href=\"https://"
"developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\" class=\"text-"
"brand-400 underline hover:text-brand-300\" target=\"_blank\">Web Crypto API</"
"a>."

msgid "Creating a Whisper"
msgstr "Opret en whisper"

msgid "You type your whisper in the browser"
msgstr "Du skriver din whisper i browseren"

msgid ""
"A random <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">AES-256-GCM</strong> key is "
"generated client-side"
msgstr ""
"En tilfældig <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">AES-256-GCM</strong>-nøgle "
"genereres på klientsiden"

msgid "Your whisper is encrypted in-browser"
msgstr "Din whisper krypteres i browseren"

msgid "Only the <em>ciphertext</em> is sent to the server"
msgstr "Kun <em>ciphertext</em> sendes til serveren"

msgid ""
"The decryption key is placed in the URL fragment (<code class=\"text-"
"brand-300\">#key</code>)"
msgstr ""
"Dekrypteringsnøglen placeres i URL-fragmentet (<code class=\"text-"
"brand-300\">#key</code>)"

msgid "Viewing a Whisper"
msgstr "Se en whisper"

msgid "You open the shared link"
msgstr "Du åbner det delte link"

msgid "The server returns the ciphertext"
msgstr "Serveren returnerer ciphertext"

msgid "The key from the URL fragment decrypts it in-browser"
msgstr "Nøglen fra URL-fragmentet dekrypterer den i browseren"

msgid "You see the plaintext — the server never does"
msgstr "Du ser klartekst — det gør serveren aldrig"

msgid "Why the URL Fragment?"
msgstr "Hvorfor URL-fragmentet?"

msgid ""
"The decryption key is stored after the <code class='bg-gray-900 px-1.5 "
"py-0.5 rounded text-brand-300'>#</code> in the URL. Per the HTTP "
"specification, <strong class='text-white'>the URL fragment is never sent to "
"the server</strong> — it's processed only by the browser. This means:"
msgstr ""
"Dekrypteringsnøglen gemmes efter <code class='bg-gray-900 px-1.5 py-0.5 "
"rounded text-brand-300'>#</code> i URL'en. Ifølge HTTP-specifikationen "
"<strong class='text-white'>sendes URL-fragmentet aldrig til serveren</"
"strong> — det behandles kun af browseren. Det betyder:"

msgid "The server never receives the decryption key"
msgstr "Serveren modtager aldrig dekrypteringsnøglen"

msgid "The key doesn't appear in server logs or analytics"
msgstr "Nøglen fremgår ikke af serverlogs eller analyseværktøjer"

msgid "Even if the server is compromised, your whispers remain encrypted"
msgstr "Selv hvis serveren kompromitteres, forbliver dine whispers krypterede"

msgid "Password Protection"
msgstr "Adgangskodebeskyttelse"

msgid ""
"Optionally, you can set a password when creating a whisper. When a password "
"is used:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan valgfrit angive en adgangskode, når du opretter en whisper. Når der "
"bruges en adgangskode:"

msgid ""
"The encryption key is derived from your password using <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-200\">PBKDF2</strong> (600,000 iterations, SHA-256)"
msgstr ""
"Krypteringsnøglen udledes af din adgangskode ved hjælp af <strong "
"class=\"text-gray-200\">PBKDF2</strong> (600.000 iterationer, SHA-256)"

msgid ""
"A random <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">salt</strong> is generated and "
"stored on the server (useless without the password)"
msgstr ""
"Der genereres en tilfældig <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">salt</strong>, "
"som gemmes på serveren (ubrugelig uden adgangskoden)"

msgid ""
"The URL contains <em>no key fragment</em> — only the password holder can "
"decrypt"
msgstr ""
"URL'en indeholder <em>intet nøglefragment</em> — kun den, der kender "
"adgangskoden, kan dekryptere"

msgid "This provides an extra layer of security for highly sensitive data"
msgstr "Det giver et ekstra sikkerhedslag til meget følsomme data"

msgid "Security Features"
msgstr "Sikkerhedsfunktioner"

msgid "Burn After Reading"
msgstr "Slet efter læsning"

msgid ""
"Whispers marked as burn-after-read are <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanently deleted</strong> the moment they are viewed — not "
"just flagged, but gone."
msgstr ""
"Whispers markeret til sletning efter læsning bliver <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanent slettet fra hukommelsen</strong> i det øjeblik, de "
"bliver vist — ikke bare markeret, men væk."

msgid ""
"Whispers marked as burn-after-read are <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanently erased from memory</strong> the moment they are "
"viewed — not just flagged, but gone."
msgstr ""
"Whispers markeret til sletning efter læsning bliver <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanent slettet fra hukommelsen</strong> i det øjeblik, de "
"bliver vist — ikke bare markeret, men væk."

msgid "Auto-Expiry"
msgstr "Automatisk udløb"

msgid ""
"All whispers require an expiration time (5 minutes to 1 month). Expired "
"whispers are automatically evicted from Redis via TTL and continuously "
"purged by a background process."
msgstr ""
"Alle whispers kræver en udløbstid (5 minutter til 1 måned). Udløbne whispers "
"fjernes automatisk fra Redis via TTL og ryddes løbende af en baggrundsproces."

msgid ""
"Industry-standard authenticated encryption. Provides both confidentiality "
"and integrity — any tampering with the ciphertext is detected."
msgstr ""
"Industristandard autentificeret kryptering. Giver både fortrolighed og "
"integritet — enhver manipulering af ciphertext opdages."

msgid "Zero Knowledge"
msgstr "Intet-kendskab"

msgid ""
"The server stores only ciphertext, IV, and optional salt in Redis. It has no "
"ability to decrypt your data, even under compulsion."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer kun ciphertext, IV og eventuel salt — og kun i flygtig "
"hukommelse (Redis). Den har ingen mulighed for at dekryptere dine data, selv "
"under tvang."

msgid ""
"The server stores only ciphertext, IV, and optional salt — and only in "
"volatile memory (Redis). It has no ability to decrypt your data, even under "
"compulsion."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer kun ciphertext, IV og eventuel salt — og kun i flygtig "
"hukommelse (Redis). Den har ingen mulighed for at dekryptere dine data, selv "
"under tvang."

msgid "What the Server Stores"
msgstr "Hvad serveren gemmer"

msgid "Redis (with persistence enabled)"
msgstr ""

msgid "Redis (in-memory only — never touches disk)"
msgstr "Redis (kun i hukommelsen — skriver aldrig til disk)"

msgid "Field"
msgstr "Felt"

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Formål"

msgid "Your encrypted data (useless without the key)"
msgstr "Dine krypterede data (ubrugelige uden nøglen)"

msgid "Random initialization vector for AES-GCM"
msgstr "Tilfældig initialiseringsvektor til AES-GCM"

msgid "PBKDF2 salt (only if password-protected)"
msgstr "PBKDF2-salt (kun hvis adgangskodebeskyttet)"

msgid "PostgreSQL (metadata only)"
msgstr "PostgreSQL (kun metadata)"

msgid "When the whisper will be auto-deleted"
msgstr "Hvornår whisperen slettes automatisk"

msgid "Number of allowed reveals before destruction (1 = burn; 0 = unlimited)"
msgstr "Antal tilladte visninger før sletning (1 = slet efter læsning; 0 = ubegrænset)"

msgid "Send or receive"
msgstr "Send eller modtag"

msgid "IP/CIDR restriction"
msgstr "IP/CIDR-begrænsning"

msgid ""
"The server does <strong>not</strong> store: plaintext, encryption keys, "
"passwords, or any identifying information. Encrypted data is stored in Redis "
"with persistence enabled."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer <strong>ikke</strong>: klartekst, krypteringsnøgler, "
"adgangskoder eller identificerende oplysninger. Krypterede data findes i "
"redis med vedvarende datalagring"

msgid ""
"The server does <strong>not</strong> store: plaintext, encryption keys, "
"passwords, or any identifying information. Encrypted data lives only in "
"volatile memory and is lost if Redis restarts."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer <strong>ikke</strong>: klartekst, krypteringsnøgler, "
"adgangskoder eller identificerende oplysninger. Krypterede data findes kun i "
"flygtig hukommelse og går tabt, hvis Redis genstarter."

msgid "Tech Stack"
msgstr "Teknologistak"

msgid "Redis (persistent)"
msgstr "Redis (vedvarende)"

msgid "Redis (in-memory)"
msgstr "Redis (i hukommelse)"

msgid "Create a whisper"
msgstr "Opret en whisper"

msgid "Whisper Burned"
msgstr "Whisper brændt"

msgid "This whisper has been burned"
msgstr "Denne whisper er brændt"

msgid ""
"This was a burn-after-reading whisper and has already been viewed. It no "
"longer exists."
msgstr ""
"Dette var en whisper med sletning efter læsning og den er allerede blevet "
"vist. Den findes ikke længere."

msgid "Create a new whisper"
msgstr "Opret en ny whisper"

